<subSubSection id="E804776EDF983B063A2C17241B97DDE7" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" type="description">
<paragraph id="5D57BDFACC3CA185109967BB633571C1" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="B6CDBFFF82FA5523616928B1350EEA01" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="5CC6C800E273658C0453142FBF31B218" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr.5) durch das folgende Merkmal: 
<emphasis id="6DE6D353AB9FEDC653F50806F36145F3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Rispe einseitswendig, zusammengezogen;</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="1A7493AA675372CAD851A25946C9616B" originalValue="Rispenäste" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Rispenaeste</normalizedToken>
aufrecht. - 
<normalizedToken id="AB8C0D434A32A662EEF17D36FF395DED" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="099211D1F1A0303BD0BDE949D6094D59" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="D89DFA86E94EAB538CC80E49E1FC7188" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="ACAF2DEB6672DA456EA5E5C9CABB87E5" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="6AF6304C8AE1311ACE0C9B7941C2010D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="A87537FDCF7C379174D47C159DE1A478" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="B9C480BCEAAEF3199F91C28F3F995078" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5). Als Unkraut gelegentlich mit 
<taxonomicName id="32CFE3E6A4FA7BE71C62412316087F2E" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="C8C58D5792D11CD732B21A6B3522F941" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
zusammen, 
<normalizedToken id="E38DFF199821E217CDFB7CA1EF6CA760" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">frueher</normalizedToken>
angebaut.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AF88F8436F6846C2DCD497A94E7EC3F2" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">
<emphasis id="2B723DB22B30C5DFF4D6D48A16F1C675" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="8197B56FCE456F7D1318AB70BD92426F" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avena" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="F6C2BFF5A40B46D5C0615367D4EF9BF4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="299">A. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5).
</paragraph>
